lead_paragraph: Belarus tennis ace Victoria Azarenka was more refined than former Australian cricketer Keith Miller when it came to dismissing concerns about pressure in sport, but the sentiment was similar.

headline.print_headline: Confident Azarenka Dismisses Pressure Like Her Opponents
